<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>فِيها تُسَمَّى سَلْسَبِيلًا ١٨ ١٤/ ٧٨<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>